com.artisan.powerhooks
Class PowerHookExperimentDetails

java.lang.Object
  com.artisan.incodeapi.ExperimentDetails
      com.artisan.powerhooks.PowerHookExperimentDetails

public class PowerHookExperimentDetails
extends ExperimentDetails

Contains information about a Power Hook experiment.

This does not include the current experimental value for the Power Hook variable or block. To get the current values use the appropriate methods on PowerHookManager.

Instead of creating PowerHookExperimentDetails objects directly, it's better to use the methods defined in PowerHookManager.
